---
// TheGateway.astro - Homepage Version
// Block 5: The Growth Blueprint
---

<section id="the-gateway" class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 md:p-8 snap-start relative border-t border-surface/30 section-pt">
  
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto w-full pt-8 pb-4 md:pt-12 md:pb-8 lg:pt-16 lg:pb-12 text-center">
    
    <h2 class="text-xs md:text-sm font-body font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-accent mb-6">
      How We Begin
    </h2>
    
    <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-[5rem] font-heading font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] leading-[1.1] text-text-heading mb-8">
      Let's build the plan that gets your investors excited again.
    </h3>
    
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-text-body text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
      <p>
        Everything starts with the <strong class="text-text-heading">Digital Presence & Growth Blueprint.</strong> This fixed-price audit is a deep-dive analysis that results in a projected growth model and a 180-day execution roadmap. This is the document you take to your next board meeting to show you know the problem and the solution.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-6">
      <a href="/services/website-growth-audit" class="btn bg-accent text-primary-base px-10 py-5 hover:bg-white text-lg min-w-48">
        Start the Growth Blueprint
      </a>
      
      <div class="pt-6 border-t border-surface/50 w-full max-w-md">
        <h4 class="text-sm text-text-body mb-4 italic font-body">
          Once the blueprint is approved...
        </h4>
        <a href="/services/website-audit-implementation" class="text-accent uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-sm hover:text-white underline underline-offset-4 decoration-accent/30 hover:decoration-white transition-colors">
          Explore the Implementation Service
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
  </div>

</section>
